00:31:22,040 --> 00:31:24,040
108結婚紀念日

451
00:31:24,040 --> 00:31:26,040
59 years for Dee

452
00:31:26,040 --> 00:31:31,040
59 years for me

453
00:31:31,040 --> 00:31:34,040
加起來108結婚週年

454
00:31:34,040 --> 00:31:36,040
but when we

455
00:31:36,040 --> 00:31:38,040
were getting engaged

456
00:31:38,040 --> 00:31:40,040
in bible school

457
00:31:40,040 --> 00:31:43,040
you had to have permission

458
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:47,040
of the dean of students

459
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:49,040
and before

460
00:31:49,040 --> 00:31:52,040
when we were trying to get it

461
00:31:52,040 --> 00:31:55,040
the dean of women

462
00:31:55,040 --> 00:31:58,040
called the interoffice

463
00:31:58,040 --> 00:31:59,040
and told her

464
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:04,040
don't marry Dick Eastman

465
00:32:04,040 --> 00:32:06,040
I don't know if she said this

466
00:32:06,040 --> 00:32:07,040
but implied it

467
00:32:07,040 --> 00:32:13,040
he is clearly a loser

468
00:32:13,040 --> 00:32:18,040
and she had to make a decision

469
00:32:18,040 --> 00:32:20,040
I don't know how it happened

470
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:24,040
but we ended up getting married

471
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:26,040
well years later

472
00:32:26,040 --> 00:32:28,040
when I faced the decision

473
00:32:28,040 --> 00:32:30,040
of joining the ministry

474
00:32:30,040 --> 00:32:32,040
of every home for Christ

475
00:32:32,040 --> 00:32:35,040
because it was not a ministry

476
00:32:35,040 --> 00:32:38,040
of our denomination

477
00:32:38,040 --> 00:32:40,040
and I had been a youth pastor

478
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:43,040
in Sacramento

479
00:32:43,040 --> 00:32:45,040
and then we started a prayer ministry

480
00:32:45,040 --> 00:32:48,040
for young people

481
00:32:48,040 --> 00:32:49,040
but we still attended

482
00:32:49,040 --> 00:32:50,040
the same church

483
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:51,040
and Dee was still very active

484
00:32:51,040 --> 00:32:53,040
in the music

485
00:32:53,040 --> 00:32:55,040
and the pastor really

486
00:32:55,040 --> 00:32:57,040
didn't want to lose Dee

487
00:32:57,040 --> 00:32:59,040
he didn't care about me

488
00:32:59,040 --> 00:33:01,040
but I remember exactly

489
00:33:01,040 --> 00:33:03,040
where I was standing

490
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:05,040
and he says

491
00:33:05,040 --> 00:33:06,040
Dick I want to just

492
00:33:06,040 --> 00:33:08,040
share my heart with you

493
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:11,040
and I believe it's from the Lord

494
00:33:11,040 --> 00:33:13,040
if you go to that ministry

495
00:33:13,040 --> 00:33:15,040
within six months

496
00:33:15,040 --> 00:33:17,040
you'll be out of the ministry

497
00:33:17,040 --> 00:33:19,040
and it will ruin

498
00:33:19,040 --> 00:33:21,040
your ministry life

499
00:33:21,040 --> 00:33:25,040
and nothing will come of it

500
00:33:25,040 --> 00:33:28,040
and I had to face the decision

501
00:33:28,040 --> 00:33:30,040
whether to move there

502
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:32,040
or go to the ministry or not

503
00:33:32,040 --> 00:33:35,040
and I went back to Wisconsin

504
00:33:35,040 --> 00:33:37,040
to talk to my father

505
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:40,040
who had very serious

506
00:33:40,040 --> 00:33:42,040
rheumatoid arthritis then

507
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:45,040
I did not tell him I was coming

508
00:33:45,040 --> 00:33:49,040
and they still lived in the trailer

509
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:51,040
I was raised in a house trailer

510
00:33:51,040 --> 00:33:53,040
all my life even through high school

511
00:33:53,040 --> 00:33:56,040
and they were in the front bedroom

512
00:33:56,040 --> 00:33:58,040
of that house trailer

513
00:33:58,040 --> 00:34:02,040
and when I went into the bedroom

514
00:34:02,040 --> 00:34:06,040
my father's back was to me

515
00:34:06,040 --> 00:34:09,040
my father's back was to me

516
00:34:09,040 --> 00:34:11,040
he was facing the wall

517
00:34:11,040 --> 00:34:14,040
and I just said dad it's Dick

518
00:34:14,040 --> 00:34:18,040
and he started to say Dick

519
00:34:18,040 --> 00:34:21,040
Dick is that really you

520
00:34:21,040 --> 00:34:23,040
I said yes dad

521
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:26,040
I came to ask you a question

522
00:34:26,040 --> 00:34:28,040
and he slowly turned

523
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:31,040
and I said dad you don't have to turn

524
00:34:31,040 --> 00:34:33,040
he just kept turning

525
00:34:33,040 --> 00:34:36,040
because he wanted to see me

526
00:34:36,040 --> 00:34:39,040
and I sat in a folding chair

527
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:43,040
and I said dad I have to make a decision

528
00:34:43,040 --> 00:34:45,040
you know the PERS center

529
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:47,040
I started for young people

530
00:34:47,040 --> 00:34:50,040
I said now I've been invited

531
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:52,040
to another ministry

532
00:34:52,040 --> 00:34:54,040
and I told him about this ministry

533
00:34:54,040 --> 00:34:57,040
I never knew that I would be

534
00:34:57,040 --> 00:34:59,040
the president of it one day

535
00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:03,040
for 34 years

536
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:05,040
but I said dad

537
00:35:05,040 --> 00:35:08,040
I need to make a decision

538
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:10,040
what would you do

539
00:35:10,040 --> 00:35:13,040
and I remember him

540
00:35:13,040 --> 00:35:15,040
raising his crippled hand

541
00:35:15,040 --> 00:35:18,040
I remember him raising his crippled hand

542
00:35:18,040 --> 00:35:21,040
that hand he used to use all the time

543
00:35:21,040 --> 00:35:23,040
to point at me don't do this

544
00:35:23,040 --> 00:35:27,040
and raised his hand so slowly

545
00:35:27,040 --> 00:35:31,040
and he started to do that

546
00:35:31,040 --> 00:35:34,040
he said Dick

547
00:35:34,040 --> 00:35:36,040
Dick

548
00:35:36,040 --> 00:35:39,040
it does not matter

549
00:35:39,040 --> 00:35:41,040
whether you stay there

550
00:35:41,040 --> 00:35:43,040
or whether you go there

551
00:35:43,040 --> 00:35:46,040
what matters

552
00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:50,040
is never lose the touch

553
00:35:50,040 --> 00:35:52,040
of the holy spirit on your life

554
00:35:52,040 --> 00:35:57,040
because if you have that

555
00:35:57,040 --> 00:36:00,040
you'll do the right thing

556
00:36:00,040 --> 00:36:04,040
so Dick risked marrying me

557
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:07,040
and together we risked

558
00:36:07,040 --> 00:36:09,040
coming to the ministry

559
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:13,040
I just want to encourage you

560
00:36:13,040 --> 00:36:16,040
even in your giving

561
00:36:16,040 --> 00:36:20,040
to support what's happening

562
00:36:20,040 --> 00:36:23,040
take a step of faith

563
00:36:23,040 --> 00:36:26,040
and watch how God will bless you

564
00:36:26,040 --> 00:36:29,040
amen

